Event Details:

Join the Stanford Conservation Program in a day dedicated to caring for Lagunita! Help us weed, pick up trash, collect data, and more! Music, snacks, and a surprise or two! Meet at the Lagunita BBQ Pit. Please RSVP at: https://forms.gle/5iqSLrWmzK8JRfKi9
